{
  "texts": [
    "The F1-score is particularly useful for evaluating models in imbalanced datasets, where the cost of false positives and false negatives may differ significantly.",
    "By employing these metrics, we ensure a balanced and thorough evaluation of the spam detection capabilities of ChatGPT-4 and Google Gemini.",
    "D. Experiment DesignThe experimental setup was designed to provide a fair and rigorous comparison between ChatGPT-4 and Google Gemini.",
    "The SpamAssassin dataset was divided into three subsets: training, validation, and testing, with a distribution of 60%, 20%, and 20% respectively.",
    "This split ensured that both models were trained on a comprehensive set of data, validated to tune hyperparameters, and finally tested on unseen data to simulate real-world performance."
  ]
}